                            <comment id="13862557" author="tilman" created="Sun, 5 Jan 2014 13:47:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Wow great! It works for two files (&quot;bimbo&quot; and &quot;foris&quot; files), but does not work for two (page 3 of the &quot;1822&quot; file, and the &quot;centerplan&quot; file of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-615&quot; title=&quot;shfill operator needs implementation&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-615&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-615&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, see near the bottom left at &quot;und M&#252;lheim die Linien 138 und 145&quot;, the &quot;&#252;&quot; is missing. Did the 1822 file work for you? (I ask to be sure that I didn&apos;t simply forgot something) Look for the number &quot;12&quot; in the middle of the image, at the left there&apos;s a missing &quot;&#246;&quot;, at the right the &quot;&#252;&quot;s are missing but the &quot;&#228;&quot; are all there?!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13862560" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 5 Jan 2014 13:58:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; I already found the problem and modified the patch. I&apos;m going to commit it soon &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And, yes, the improvement is cool!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13862575" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 5 Jan 2014 15:42:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I added the proposed patch in revision 1555529 with some slight changes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;the deprecated endchar command may occur with 4 and 5 numbers, the origin patch handles only the 5 number case correct&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;some reformatting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;A big thanks for the contribution!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13862616" author="jahewson" created="Sun, 5 Jan 2014 18:11:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I forgot about the 1822 file, well spotted!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13862624" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 5 Jan 2014 18:44:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just for those who are interested in the details:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve changed line 135 in Type2CharString&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;from&lt;br/&gt;
            numbers = clearStack(numbers, numbers.size()  &amp;gt; 0);&lt;br/&gt;
to&lt;br/&gt;
            numbers = clearStack(numbers, numbers.size() == 5);&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13862635" author="tilman" created="Sun, 5 Jan 2014 19:09:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, it all works now. And there doesn&apos;t seem to be any negative side effect on any of my test files.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
